data.description: A stained deck provides a scenic view of the backyard featuring a BASKETBALL COURT for those who enjoy staying active & having fun outdoors. The interior has that new home smell w/new interior paint & carpet. The heart of the home, the kitchen, boasts timeless oak flat panel cabinets that provide both ample storage & a touch of warmth. The decorative backsplash adds a touch of visual intrigue, while the stainless steel appliances, including a smooth cooktop, built-in microwave, & dishwasher, ensure both style & functionality. The master suite is a haven of relaxation. With its vaulted ceiling, it exudes an air of spaciousness, & the walk-in closet ensures ample storage. The adjoining master bath is a sanctuary in its own right, featuring a dual vanity, garden tub perfect for unwinding, a separate shower for a quick revitalization. Comfortable family room offers a fireplace featuring custom mantel with dentil trim & ceiling fan with a light kit. Working from home is a breeze with the first-floor office, complete with glass French doors & hardwood floors that offer both privacy & professionalism.
